Source: Surfeit of Lampreys
Author: MARSH
Vol / Page: ix 127
Edition:
Quote: And Miss Grey still sat erect on her stool. Alleyn was reminded of the childish game of Steps in which whenever the `he' has his back turned, the players creep nearer, only to freeze into immobility whenever he turns round and faces them.
